      "text": "AKS + InfiniBand GPU fabric, serving on Azure, Microsoft Entra Workload Identity. The Azure NETWORKING fabric (highlighted blue) is the spine: VNet, Azure CNI (Cilium), Private Link, Front Door, Firewall, hub-spoke.",
